00:32:15,699 --> 00:32:24,379
Thank you for those that, Lord, suffered greatly, persecution, great adversities, but they continued.

647
00:32:24,379 --> 00:32:26,699
They remained steadfast.

648
00:32:26,699 --> 00:32:29,339
Lord, I thank you for my salvation.

