00:32:33,979 --> 00:32:43,940
And God, I pray that as we consider the instruction from 1 Thessalonians chapter 5 this evening,

652
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:50,099
as we conclude that text and consider a healthy church, God, would you help us to take all

653
00:32:50,099 --> 00:32:56,019
that we've learned over these many weeks and apply it, that we'd be doers of the word and

654
00:32:56,019 --> 00:33:02,940
not hearers only, that we would be a church that's a healthy church.

